            <title>[LU-4418] Test failure on test suite conf-sanity, subtest test_47</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4418</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Jinshan Xiong &amp;lt;jinshan.xiong@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/af9148c4-6f08-11e3-ad93-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/af9148c4-6f08-11e3-ad93-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_47 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test failed to respond and timed out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 47&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Recovery failed on the OST because one client couldn&apos;t be recovered until timeout&lt;/p&gt;</description>
